    "description": [
        "Episode of Series \"Discussing Controversial Issues\". By providing topics for discussion teachers acting as moderators in separate classrooms show how a discussion can be productively carried out. The film clearly shows the jobs of both the moderator and the participants. Shows how to develop an open (non-threatening) situation in which meaningful discussions can take place."
